---
title: Pesto & Cheddar-Crusted Chicken with Roasted Kumara & Garden Salad
description: Basil pesto is the secret ingredient in this recipe! It not only adds delicious flavour to the chicken, but also acts as the glue for the Cheddar crust! Roasted kumara and a fresh garden salad complete this easy weeknight winner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/parmesan-pesto-crusted-chicken-f8d9cfa2.jpg
